Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.31,0:00:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么发现？迪克
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.79,0:00:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试了各种方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奈这里的器材有限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那东西确实了得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体的反应速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非我军机动战士能比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定满载着各种超乎想象的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为武器可谓完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 菲利特那边进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初步看来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是强制激发X-Rounder能力的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用脉冲磁场刺激脑内X-Rounder领域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让机师发挥出部分类似X-Rounder的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强制激活X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能会对大脑造成恶性影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.56,0:01:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长期使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.93,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会伤及机师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.48,0:01:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详情只能等死亡机师的验尸报告
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的机动战士外加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激发机师X-Rounder能力的头盔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.81,0:01:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克继续分析
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须报告BIGRING
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活X-Rounder的头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了那个头盔 我也能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.11,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:03:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等大家看完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再慢慢看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.03,0:04:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是战争…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为自己明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是看到敌人死掉的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才重新意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们机师随时会死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…随时都会下达出击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一去不回
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不留下遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.94,0:04:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不留下想做却没做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说！我有事想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说可能会让人觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也没有一起外出过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进餐都在舰上食堂…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.74,0:05:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想说的是…重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…你想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢斯上士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}结婚好吗～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日野司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我用那头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那头盔 如果真可以激发X-Rounder能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.69,0:05:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 一定能杀更多敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那头盔很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让你用它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定可以变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是杰哈特…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.66,0:06:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 伊泽尔坎特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻略BIGRING的失败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有责任都在我这个指挥官身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愿承受任何处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的计划考虑到了任何一种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIGRING攻略战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最低限度的战略目标已经达成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集到了足够多的素材判断地球军军力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的部署
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应变能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X-Rounder的战斗力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.27,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲不是没有价值的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那些数据为依据
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.76,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的入侵作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的…入侵作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的作战不会失败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们开始吧 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们期待已久的 新世界的构建
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个节骨眼上禁止出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为戈林和泽尔报仇的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长也赞成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下个作战计划成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也会重新整编加入战队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人就必须服从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 您脑子没秀逗吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个毛头指挥官和我们的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个更重要 有得比吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞同蕾西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是X-Rounder中的精英
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八魔人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我们做缩头乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与美学相去甚远
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是相同意见吗 敏克
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 倒不如说我第一个想冲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己呢？ 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会真的想阻拦我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.36,0:08:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 这话题很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的话你都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无视命令擅自出击 这可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说要告发你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上我一起…没意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是达乌内斯司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.33,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人允许他们出击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西尔·加勒特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克·雷丁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.61,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾西·阿德涅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷奥·路易斯 四人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让他们回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由他去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匆忙通信会被联邦察觉我们的行动
