Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人哨机R-33 S-31
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探测到红移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无人哨机T30 发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与维甘舰船热谱一致
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.27,0:09:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明日野司令料事如神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的目标多半是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺德拉姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是地球圈防线上不容有失的中轨道卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括武器生产在内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各功能集于一身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺德拉姆一旦有失
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的战略会土崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人侵略地球会变得轻而易举
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以赶忙离开索伦城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯正率军前往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰也须在作战中出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索敌系统有感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B442发现不明机体 数量4
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维甘的机动战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找你了 菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 陪我玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德西尔和X-Rounder部队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 一级战斗部署
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.41,0:10:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机动战士部队紧急出击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}重复 全员一级战斗部署…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 敌人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说黑的那个也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 X-Rounder…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.38,0:11:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆又迟到？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.72,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 敌人是X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别离开我的视线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔夫·安尼克 G-Bouncer出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚开 杂兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的对手是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来就连船一起砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主炮 速射模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉数听我指示
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射间隔设为每秒1
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行动被看穿了 德西尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE2在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还不出击？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿它做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想戴上它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 让我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为击败维甘的X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要对抗X-Rounder的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西会毁了你的脑子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡思乱想 快去机库
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:13:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了白的 全是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是两台蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克斯少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿莉莎 麦克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.27,0:14:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去吧 地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.16,0:15:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华美地散去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高达！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克斯少尉和阿莉莎后退
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.65,0:15:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来晚了 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就让他返航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这种情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能让他继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢 竟敢让我美丽的机体负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有空东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 X-Rounder的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞧不起人 地球种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.80,0:17:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我竟然…这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不美！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.72,0:17:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷奥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢对雷奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳命来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.83,0:18:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏克姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嚣张了 可恶的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我劣势？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 八魔人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你什么预判能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子靠的是技术含量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾西！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 继续孤立无援的战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己在干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是让自己置身于危险中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可能殃及所有战友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再违抗命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么想当X-Rounder吗？ 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不那么做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连父亲 也超越不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.25,0:20:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成不了X-Rounder的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你成为超级机师亚瑟姆·明日野就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级…机师？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是X-Rounder 但却很牛的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 我干掉了X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你之前也用高达击败过X-Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你擅长的就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得更强 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.34,0:20:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便有优秀的天赋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心理脆弱自暴自弃也成不了大器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里强的家伙才是最后的赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 别这样 鼻子会痒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用去见德西尔大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.08,0:21:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不必 作战需要进行调整
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你继续妨碍我们作战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必须被清除
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.45,0:21:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的实力 才不是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾伦格雷亚斯中校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看…看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离3500 放大显示
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
